articles.description:
I think the Comeback Era has Started from 2023 for all failed(trolled) directors. JAILER for Nelson and now MARK ANTONY for Aadhik Ravichandran. An Extraordinary Performance from SJ Suryah, of course Vishal has done his role well but SJ Suryah's performance is Clearly Dominating everything. And Main Credits goes to the Editor Vijay Velukutty, He has delivered a Very Fast paced Editing which makes the audience stick to the screen from Beginning to End. And regarding Music, GV Prakash has really made a Musical Massacre just like they said in the Trailer. Both Background Scores and Songs are really Good, and the way of using old songs in right place gives pure goosebumps. Aadhik Ravichandran has changed his Style and given a movie which will Impress The Audience of all Ages. The Best "Sci-fi & Comedy" Movie in Tamil of 2023. This Movie is a Pure "Theatre Experience Film". Don't Miss it in Theatres. 
	Rating: 4.3/5 
	 
	Join our Telegram channel for more Movie Reviews and Cine Updates

articles.description:
Sources say The Pre-Release Event for Leo movie will be held on 14th October at Kuala Lumpur, Malaysia. The Movie team is requesting Vijay to participate in this event since the Vijay fans in Malaysia are disappointed by the news that Audio Launch Event has been shifted from Malaysia to Chennai. 
	 
	 
	Latest update regarding the Mark Antony movie is that, Actor Karthi has given Voice over in the film(as a Narrator) just like Kamal Hassan did in Ponniyin Selvan. 
	 
	 
	The Second Single for Leo movie will be released on 19th September on behalf of Vinayagar Chaturthi. We can expect the Official Announcement of the 2nd single on 15th September In either Promo Video or a Tweet from the Movie Team. 
	 
	 
	Few Informations regarding the Leo's second single is that, the location of the song is Kashmir. If you notice Loki is clearly foreshadowing Fire and Ice with Vijay's Past life and present life in the movie. First single(Past Vijay) was happening inside the factory and if you notice the tone of the video it will be red which denotes Fire and you can also see a lot of fire used in the background of the song, and now the second single is happening on Kashmir and the tone of the song will be white(snow) which denotes Ice. And It is obvious that the background of the song will be Snow(ice). And also in all of Loki's Tweets whenever he mentions LEO he intentionally puts fire and ice emoji near Leo "#LEO". So there will be a huge connection between this Metaphors and the Character of Vijay in Past and present life. Loki is Cooking up something Big, Let's Wait for the Cinematic Feast on 19th October. 
	 
	Join our Telegram channel for more Exclusive Cine Updates
